==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glost oven
<hw>Glost" ov`en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>An oven in which glazed pottery
is fired; -- also called <altname>glaze kiln</altname>, or
<altname>glaze</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glottal</ent>⟦br⟧
